1
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:29,700
What a Liu Yong,

2
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:32,030
daring to withhold military rations

3
00:00:32,030 --> 00:00:33,700
and hoard weapons.

4
00:00:34,030 --> 00:00:35,500
Pass my decree.

5
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:37,430
Execute Liu Yong and his entire family.

6
00:00:37,430 --> 00:00:38,760
The crisis is resolved.

7
00:00:38,930 --> 00:00:39,560
Jingzhi.

8
00:00:39,830 --> 00:00:41,160
Liu Yong hides well.

9
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:43,600
How come the hard evidence

10
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:45,400
sprouted legs at this critical moment?

11
00:00:45,400 --> 00:00:48,530
I feel an invisible hand

12
00:00:48,530 --> 00:00:51,730
is paving the way for my Eastern Depot Commander.

13
00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:54,230
I was seen through.

14
00:00:56,330 --> 00:00:57,160
Answer me.

15
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,560
Did you kill Liu Yong

16
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:01,220
to pave the way for Ying Wujiu?

17
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:03,760
Your heart has long flown to the border.

18
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:05,960
I will ask you one last time.

19
00:01:08,130 --> 00:01:08,930
Yes.

20
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:10,800
I had it done.

21
00:01:12,930 --> 00:01:14,530
But it wasn't for Ying Wujiu.

22
00:01:15,300 --> 00:01:18,360
It was for the 134 lives of my Qu family.

23
00:01:19,330 --> 00:01:21,030
Liu Yong is Yu Henian's most loyal dog.

24
00:01:21,030 --> 00:01:21,960
He withheld military rations

25
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,960
to starve the 100,000 soldiers at the border.

26
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:24,660
If the army falls,

27
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,560
the old thief Yu Henian will march straight in

28
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,900
and seize the Dazheng empire.

29
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:30,360
Who will execute the Yu family for me then?

30
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,100
Your Majesty.

31
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:33,160
Are you going to watch those traitors

32
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,700
sever the dragon vein of your Dazheng?

33
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:35,759
Her ruthlessness

34
00:01:35,759 --> 00:01:38,000
is all for her own deep-seated vengeance.

35
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:40,160
Hahaha, good.

36
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,500
My harem is full of

37
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:44,430
jealous fools.

38
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:46,729
Only you, a defanged viper,

39
00:01:46,729 --> 00:01:49,229
dare to stab the traitors in the heart for me.

40
00:01:49,229 --> 00:01:50,400
Pass my decree.

41
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,229
Noble Lady Qu is credited with protecting me.

42
00:01:52,229 --> 00:01:53,900
She is promoted to Imperial Noble Consort

43
00:01:53,900 --> 00:01:55,759
and granted the power to co-manage the six palaces.

44
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:58,100
Jingzhi, you hate the Yu family.

45
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,759
I will use Ying Wujiu's sword

46
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:02,130
to behead the entire Yu family.

47
00:02:02,330 --> 00:02:04,160
As long as you stay by my side

48
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:06,230
as my sharpest blade.

49
00:02:06,330 --> 00:02:08,930
Ying Wujiu, the rations will arrive tomorrow.

50
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:11,000
I will wear the crown of the Imperial Noble Consort

51
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,060
and wait for your triumphant return.

52
00:02:29,930 --> 00:02:30,800
Ying Wujiu.

53
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,930
The crisis is resolved.

54
00:02:32,930 --> 00:02:34,990
The rations for the 100,000 soldiers

55
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:37,430
will reach the border tomorrow.

56
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,829
In this bloody palace,

57
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:42,960
I will wear this crown of the Imperial Noble Consort

58
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:45,020
and wait for your triumphant return.

59
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,020
Your Ladyship.

60
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:58,430
Liu Yong's family has been taken by the royal guards.

61
00:02:59,530 --> 00:03:01,260
But the deputies in the Ministry of Revenue

62
00:03:01,260 --> 00:03:02,760
are still shirking responsibility

63
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:04,360
over escorting the rations.

64
00:03:07,930 --> 00:03:08,730
Hmph.

65
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:11,460
Then I

66
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:13,560
will add fuel to their fire.

67
00:03:26,630 --> 00:03:28,630
Pass my verbal order to the shadows.

68
00:03:29,530 --> 00:03:31,700
Whoever dares to shirk tonight,

69
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:33,800
tomorrow,

70
00:03:34,060 --> 00:03:36,190
they won't need to keep their tongues.

71
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:38,100
Yes.

72
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:53,490
Before dawn,

73
00:03:54,130 --> 00:03:56,130
the rations must leave Anding Gate.

74
00:04:24,130 --> 00:04:25,360
By the master's order,

75
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,400
if the rations are here,

76
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,160
we are here.

77
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,530
Anyone who stands in the way

78
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:31,360
will be killed without mercy.

79
00:05:11,930 --> 00:05:12,830
Commander.

80
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,360
Will the supplies still arrive?

81
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,700
The men

82
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:20,290
don't even have the strength to draw their bows.

83
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:25,260
As long as I am still standing,

84
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,500
the supplies will come.
